author: Allison Carey, The Plain Dealer
title: Tracey Bradnan mixes fun with formal, creates nerd-chic wardrobe: Fashion Flash (photos, video)
text: Tracey Bradnan loves her work in marketing and walking the campus of Case Western Reserve University looking at the diverse world of fashion that exists there. She's created her own look by mixing formal and classic with preppy and punk to create a kind of nerd-chic style that brings her confidence and makes her happy.
